{
  "text": "Since the original simulation datasets represented approximately log-normal plasma and tissue concentration data, and there were a small number of tissue samples per simulation dataset, geometric mean concentrations at each time-point were generated, and geometric mean PK parameter estimates were used. Estimates of positive slopes were excluded from the individual bootstrap estimate, as per Mager and Goller [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
